    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "it just feels so heavy. like, if I could just find a way to make it stop... not just the debt, but the whole feeling of being a disaster for everyone. sometimes i think the only way to actually help them is to just stop being a factor in their lives entirely. do you think people actually get that? like, that leaving might be the only way to actually be kind to them?",
